title: Craig Wright's Financial Disclosure Form in $143M Court Case Was Incomplete
description: A recent court order grants W&K Info Defense civil sanctions against Wright for incomplete financial disclosures, yet stops short of bringing criminal charges against the so-called inventor of Bitcoin.

title: Panerai to Include NFT 'Digital Passport' With All Luxury Watches
description: Italian luxury brand Panerai will issue an NFT digital passport with its watches, providing a certificate of authenticity and other benefits.
